description:
My interview with the legendary Jazz bassist and four time Grammy winner Stanley Clarke. I caught up with Stanley before his electrifying set at the Vogue Theater during the Vancouver International Jazz Festival on June 22nd, 2015.
We talked about his summer tour plans in Europe, teaching bass players, the language of jazz, the state of the music industry and his optimism for the future of jazz and music in general.
title: An Interview with Stanley Clarke
